<https://frames.linkeddata.es/text/02013L0036-20220101/title_X__art_150#char=0,893>
    a                   nif:Context, nif:String ;
    nif:isString        "Article 21a of Directive 2002/87/EC is hereby amended as follows: Article 21a of Directive 2002/87/EC is hereby amended as follows: in paragraph 2, point (a) is deleted; paragraph 3 is replaced by the following:\"3.In order to ensure consistent application of the calculation methods listed in Annex I, Part II, of this Directive, in conjunction with Article 49(1) of Regulation (EU) No 575/2013 and Article 228(1) of Directive 2009/138/ECThe ESA shall submit those draft regulatory technical standards to the Commission by five months before the date of application referred to in Article 309(1) of Directive 2009/138/ECPower is delegated to the Commission to adopt the regulatory technical standards referred to in the first subparagraph in accordance with Articles 10 to 14 of Regulation (EU) No 1093/2010, of Regulation (EU) No 1094/2010 and of Regulation (EU) No 1095/2010 respectively. \"." ;
    nif:beginIndex      0 ;
    nif:endIndex        893 ;
    eli:cites           <http://data.europa.eu/eli/dir/2013/36/2022-01-01> .

<https://frames.linkeddata.es/text/02017R1129-20211110/chp_X__art_47__para_1#char=0,531>
    a                   nif:Context, nif:String ;
    nif:isString        "Based on the documents made public through the mechanism referred to in Article�21(6), ESMA shall publish every year a report containing statistics on the prospectuses approved and notified in the Union and an analysis of trends taking into account: the types of issuers, in particular the categories of persons referred to in points (a) to (d) of Article�15(1); and the types of issuances, in particular the total consideration of the offers, the types of transferable securities, the types of trading venue and the denominations." ;
    nif:beginIndex      0 ;
    nif:endIndex        531 ;
    eli:cites           <http://data.europa.eu/eli/reg/2017/1129/2021-11-10> .

<https://frames.linkeddata.es/text/02012R0528-20191120/chp_VIII__sec_2__art_46__para_3#char=0,195>
    a                   nif:Context, nif:String ;
    nif:isString        "Within 180 days of receipt of a recommendation from the evaluating competent authority, the Agency shall prepare and submit to the Commission an opinion on the renewal of the Union authorisation." ;
    nif:beginIndex      0 ;
